Reducing cardiovascular risk with immunomodulators: a randomised active comparator trial among patients with rheumatoid arthritis.
 We found that addition of either a TNFi or triple therapy resulted in clinically important improvements in vascular inflammation. However, the addition of a TNFi did not reduce arterial inflammation more than triple therapy.
Pubmed   Journal   ReadQx 
Arthritis Care Res (Hoboken)
    Agreement Among Multiple Observers on Crystal Identification by Synovial Fluid Microscopy.
 Compensated polarized microscopy remained consistent in detecting and identifying crystals in synovial fluid, even when examined among multiple observers, confirming its high utility for clinical practice.
Pubmed   Journal   ReadQx 
Arthritis Res Ther
    Abnormal cortical thickness and structural covariance networks in systemic lupus erythematosus patients without major neuropsychiatric manifestations.
 Extensive and obvious reduction in cortical thickness and abnormal topological organization of SCNs are observed in non-NPSLE patients. The observed abnormalities may not only be the realization of brain damage caused by the disease, but also the contribution of the compensatory changes within the nervous system.
Pubmed   Journal   ReadQx 
Autologous hematopoietic stem cell transplantation improves long-term survival-data from a national registry.
 Our analysis of real-life data show that the distribution of risk factors for mortality is critical when HSCT cohorts are compared with non-HSCT control groups.
Pubmed   Journal   ReadQx 
Epigenetic modification of miR-217 promotes intervertebral disc degeneration by targeting the FBXO21-ERK signalling pathway.
Overexpression of miR-217 inhibits IDD via FBXO21/ERK regulation.
Pubmed   Journal   ReadQx 
Four emerging immune cellular blood phenotypes associated with disease duration and activity established in Psoriatic Arthritis.
 Four immune cellular phenotypes of PsA were suggested at baseline demonstrating complex immune cellular mechanisms in PsA implying the possibility of improving PsA patient stratification based on both clinical and immune cellular phenotypes.
Pubmed   Journal   ReadQx 
Arthritis Rheumatol
    Impaired efferocytosis by synovial macrophages in patients with knee osteoarthritis.
 Apoptotic cells accumulate in the synovium of patients with late-stage knee OA. Our results suggest that OA impairs critical homeostatic functions of synovial macrophages leading to accumulation of apoptotic cells.
Pubmed   Journal   ReadQx 
Syk Activation in Circulating and Tissue Innate Immune Cells in Antineutrophil Cytoplasmic Antibody-Associated Vasculitis.
 These findings indicate that Syk plays a critical role in MPO-ANCA IgG-induced myeloid cell responses and that Syk is activated in circulating immune cells and tissue immune cells in AAV;  therefore, Syk inhibition may be a potential therapeutic option.
Pubmed   Journal   ReadQx 
